REMARKS.content:
REMARKS:  This soil was included in the Irondale series in Iron County, Missouri. Diagnostic horizons and features recognized in this series are:
ochric epipedon - the zone from the surface of the soil to a depth of 12 inches;
argillic horizon - the zone from approximately 12 to 36 inches;
fragipan - the zone from 36 inches to 80 inches.
National Cooperative Soil Survey
U.S.A.
